In our Spring/Summer 2016 issue we ve taken some of the top men s and women s fashion trends off the runway and reinterpreted them for you.Ladies, in The Edit we show you how to combine sailor stripes and nautical hues to create a statement-making summer wardrobe. While in The Edit Man we take a closer look at how local designers are bringing new perspectives to contemporary men s fashion.Then in The Edit Living we shine a spotlight on modern design movement.A print version of the 'The Edit' is sent out to select Sunday Times subscribers.